I"<h1 id="bluetooth-pairing">Bluetooth Pairing</h1>

<h2 id="1-bluez-install">1. Bluez install</h2>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>bluez libbluetooth-dev pi-bluetooth
</code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="python-36이상">Python 3.6이상</h3>
<p>Python 3.6 이후 버전은 SSL을 요구하기 떄문에 설치</p>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>libreadline-gplv2-dev libncursesw5-dev libssl-dev libsqlite3-dev tk-dev libgdbm-dev libc6-dev libbz2-dev
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="2-시리얼-포트-등록">2. 시리얼 포트 등록</h2>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>sdptool SP
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="3-bluetooth-서비스-실행옵션-수정">3. Bluetooth 서비스 실행옵션 수정</h2>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>systemctl daemon-reload
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>vi /lib/systemd/system/bluetooth.service
  <span class="c">#ExecStart=/usr/lib/bluetooth/bluetoothd -C 로 수정</span>
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>systemctl resart Bluetooth
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>systemctl <span class="nb">enable </span>Bluetooth
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="4-장치-내-블루투스-discoverable-상태로-변경">4. 장치 내 블루투스 Discoverable 상태로 변경</h2>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>hciconfig hci0 piscan
</code></pre></div></div>
